      <data key="d4">The child paper, &quot;You Only Look Once: Unified, Real-Time Object Detection,&quot; builds on the parent paper, &quot;Going Deeper with Convolutions,&quot; by utilizing the deep convolutional neural network architecture proposed in the parent work to develop a novel approach for real-time object detection. The child paper extends the concepts of the parent by framing object detection as a regression problem and optimizing the entire pipeline for performance, demonstrating improvements in speed and generalization over existing methods.</data>
