      <data key="d4">The child paper, &quot;Faster R-CNN,&quot; builds on the foundational concepts introduced in the parent paper, &quot;Going Deeper with Convolutions,&quot; by utilizing the deep convolutional neural network architecture (GoogLeNet) to enhance object detection through the introduction of Region Proposal Networks (RPN). It extends the parent paper's work by integrating advanced techniques for real-time object detection while maintaining high accuracy, thereby advancing the state-of-the-art in the field.</data>
