      <data key="d4">The child paper, &quot;Rethinking the Inception Architecture for Computer Vision,&quot; builds on the parent paper, &quot;Going Deeper with Convolutions,&quot; by exploring and extending the Inception architecture through improved efficiency and performance benchmarks, while also introducing new techniques such as factorized convolutions and aggressive regularization. The child paper references the foundational concepts of the parent paper but aims to enhance its application in practical scenarios, particularly in mobile and big-data contexts.</data>
