      <data key="d4">The child paper builds on the parent paper by proposing a new activation function, the Parametric Linear Unit (PReLU), and a robust initialization method that enhance the performance of deep convolutional networks, specifically surpassing the human-level performance established by the parent paper's GoogLeNet architecture in ImageNet classification. Additionally, it extends the findings of the parent paper by investigating deeper network architectures and improving model fitting with minimal computational cost.</data>
