      <data key="d4">The child paper builds on the parent paper by utilizing the dropout technique to enhance the training of deep rectifier networks, specifically through the introduction of the Parametric Linear Unit (PReLU) and a robust initialization method. It extends the concepts of regularization and overfitting addressed in the parent paper to achieve superior performance in image classification tasks.</data>
