      <data key="d4">The child paper on image style transfer builds on the parent paper's foundational work on fully convolutional networks by utilizing derived convolutional neural networks for high-level image representation and manipulation. It extends the concepts of feature extraction and representation from the parent paper to address the specific task of artistic style transfer, demonstrating the application of these networks in a new context.</data>
