      <data key="d4">The child paper builds on the concepts introduced in the parent paper by extending the fully convolutional network architecture to develop a Convolutional LSTM (ConvLSTM) model specifically for precipitation nowcasting. It leverages the principles of convolutional networks to enhance spatiotemporal sequence predictions, demonstrating improved performance over existing models.</data>
