      <data key="d4">The child paper builds on the parent paper by introducing the Region Proposal Network (RPN) as an enhancement to the existing object detection framework, leveraging shared convolutional features to improve proposal generation efficiency. It extends the concepts presented in the parent paper by integrating neural attention mechanisms and demonstrating superior performance metrics on benchmark datasets.</data>
