      <data key="d4">The child paper, &quot;Faster R-CNN,&quot; builds on the parent paper, &quot;Fast R-CNN,&quot; by introducing the Region Proposal Network (RPN) that enhances the object detection process through shared convolutional features, thereby improving both speed and accuracy. It extends the concepts presented in the parent paper by integrating new methodologies and achieving state-of-the-art results in object detection tasks.</data>
