      <data key="d4">The child paper builds on the parent paper by introducing a new criterion for assessing discriminant validity in variance-based structural equation modeling, which is a distinct area of statistical analysis. While the parent paper focuses on multiple test procedures, the child paper extends the discussion by proposing an alternative approach to validity assessment, demonstrating its effectiveness through simulation studies.</data>
