      <data key="d3">In 2015, article Batch Normalization: Accelerating Deep Network Training by Reducing Internal Covariate Shift was published and referenced article Understanding the difficulty of training deep feedforward neural networks that was published in 2010</data>
      <data key="d4">The child paper on Batch Normalization builds on the parent paper's exploration of training difficulties in deep neural networks by addressing the issue of internal covariate shift, which the parent paper identifies as a challenge in training. The child paper extends the parent’s findings by introducing a novel normalization technique that significantly accelerates training and improves performance in deep learning models.</data>
