      <data key="d4">The child paper reviews and summarizes various statistical pattern recognition techniques, including those related to machine learning, while the parent paper introduces and evaluates a specific boosting algorithm, AdaBoost, within the context of machine learning. The child paper builds on the foundational concepts of pattern recognition discussed in the parent paper by situating them within a broader review of statistical methodologies and applications.</data>
