      <data key="d4">The child paper builds on the parent paper by applying the principles of boosting algorithms, specifically in the context of boosted regression trees (BRT), to address ecological modeling challenges. It extends the concepts introduced in the parent paper by demonstrating the practical application of boosting techniques in ecological data analysis, while also providing a tutorial for ecologists.</data>
