      <data key="d4">The child paper, &quot;Learning Deep Architectures for AI,&quot; builds on the foundational concepts of machine learning introduced in the parent paper, &quot;Experiments with a new boosting algorithm,&quot; by exploring advanced architectures and algorithms that enhance learning capabilities in AI. While the parent paper focuses on a specific boosting algorithm and its experimental results, the child paper extends this work by discussing the necessity of deep architectures for achieving high-level abstractions in AI tasks.</data>
