      <data key="d4">The child paper on extreme learning machines builds on the concepts of neural network training by proposing a novel algorithm that addresses the slow learning speed associated with traditional methods, thereby extending the foundational ideas of machine learning presented in the parent paper. While the parent paper focuses on boosting algorithms and their performance, the child paper introduces a distinct approach to enhance learning efficiency in feedforward neural networks.</data>
