      <data key="d4">The child paper, &quot;EfficientDet: Scalable and Efficient Object Detection,&quot; builds on the parent paper, &quot;EfficientNet: Rethinking Model Scaling for Convolutional Neural Networks,&quot; by utilizing the EfficientNet backbones and applying the proposed scaling methods to develop a new family of object detection models that achieve superior performance and efficiency. The child paper extends the concepts introduced in the parent paper by implementing optimizations specific to object detection tasks.</data>
