      <data key="d3">In 2017, article Towards Evaluating the Robustness of Neural Networks was published and referenced article Intriguing properties of neural networks that was published in 2014</data>
      <data key="d4">The child paper builds on the findings of the parent paper by addressing the vulnerabilities of neural networks to adversarial examples, specifically challenging the robustness claims made in the parent paper. It extends the discussion by introducing new attack algorithms that demonstrate the limitations of defensive distillation methods proposed in the context of neural network robustness.</data>
