      <data key="d4">The child paper builds on the parent paper by extending the RNN Encoder-Decoder model to a more general end-to-end sequence-to-sequence learning approach using Long Short-Term Memory (LSTM) networks, while also comparing its performance against the parent paper's statistical machine translation system.</data>
