      <data key="d4">The child paper, &quot;Dynamic Graph CNN for Learning on Point Clouds,&quot; builds on the foundational concepts introduced in the parent paper, &quot;PointNet++: Deep Hierarchical Feature Learning on Point Sets in a Metric Space,&quot; by proposing a new network module (EdgeConv) that enhances feature learning on point clouds through dynamic graph structures. While the parent paper focuses on hierarchical feature learning, the child paper extends this work by incorporating local neighborhood information and addressing topological aspects, thereby enriching the model's ability to capture semantic characteristics in point cloud data.</data>
