      <data key="d4">The child paper, &quot;YOLOv4: Optimal Speed and Accuracy of Object Detection,&quot; builds on the foundational concepts of deep learning architectures introduced in the parent paper, &quot;SqueezeNet: AlexNet-level accuracy with 50x fewer parameters and &lt;0.5MB model size,&quot; by incorporating advanced features and techniques to enhance object detection performance. While the parent paper focuses on model size and efficiency, the child paper extends this work by applying new methodologies to achieve state-of-the-art accuracy in real-time object detection.</data>
