      <data key="d4">The child paper on TensorFlow builds on the foundational concepts of machine learning and neural networks established in the parent paper about large-scale video classification with Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs). While the parent paper focuses on empirical evaluations of CNNs for video classification, the child paper extends this work by providing a flexible framework (TensorFlow) for implementing and executing various machine learning algorithms, including those based on CNNs.</data>
