      <data key="d4">The child paper builds on the parent paper by extending the application of Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) from 3D action recognition in surveillance videos to large-scale video classification, incorporating new techniques for spatio-temporal information processing. It also empirically evaluates the performance of its proposed methods against the baseline established by the parent paper, demonstrating significant improvements in classification accuracy.</data>
