      <data key="d3">In 2012, article Data mining: concepts and techniques was published and referenced article An efficient k-means clustering algorithm: analysis and implementation that was published in 2002</data>
      <data key="d4">The child paper builds on the concepts introduced in the parent paper by expanding the discussion of data mining techniques, including clustering methods like k-means, and integrating new topics such as data warehouses and social networks. It serves as a comprehensive resource that not only references the parent paper's findings but also enhances the understanding and application of data mining in various fields.</data>
