      <data key="d4">The child paper, &quot;Survey of Clustering Algorithms,&quot; builds on the parent paper, &quot;An efficient k-means clustering algorithm: analysis and implementation,&quot; by providing a broader overview of clustering algorithms, including k-means, and discussing their applications across various fields. While the child paper references the parent paper's findings, it extends the discussion to include additional clustering methods and related topics, rather than simply comparing performance or experimental results.</data>
