      <data key="d4">The child paper on Generative Adversarial Nets (GANs) builds on the theoretical foundations of deep architectures discussed in the parent paper, applying these principles to propose a novel framework for generative modeling through adversarial training. It extends the concepts of deep learning by introducing a specific application that leverages deep architectures to improve generative model performance.</data>
