      <data key="d4">The child paper, &quot;Deep Learning in Medical Image Analysis,&quot; builds on the foundational concepts presented in the parent paper, &quot;Learning Deep Architectures for AI,&quot; by applying deep learning techniques to the specific domain of medical imaging. It extends the parent paper's discussion of deep architectures by exploring their practical applications and successes in medical image analysis, while also suggesting future research directions in this field.</data>
