    <edge source="https://openalex.org/W2025768430" target="https://openalex.org/W2153663612">
      <data key="d3">In 2008, article Extracting and composing robust features with denoising autoencoders was published and referenced article Image Denoising Via Sparse and Redundant Representations Over Learned Dictionaries that was published in 2006</data>
      <data key="d4">The child paper builds on the parent paper by introducing denoising autoencoders as a method for extracting robust features, leveraging the concepts of representation and noise handling discussed in the parent paper. It extends the parent paper's findings by proposing a new training principle that enhances the robustness of learned representations through partial corruption of input patterns.</data>
      <data key="d5">3</data>
      <data key="d6">G1723</data>
