      <data key="d4">The child paper, &quot;BART: Denoising Sequence-to-Sequence Pre-training for Natural Language Generation, Translation, and Comprehension,&quot; builds on the concepts introduced in the parent paper, &quot;XLNet: Generalized Autoregressive Pretraining for Language Understanding,&quot; by exploring denoising sequence-to-sequence pre-training techniques for natural language tasks, thereby extending the foundational ideas of autoregressive modeling and pre-training methodologies.</data>
