      <data key="d4">The child paper, &quot;YOLOv4: Optimal Speed and Accuracy of Object Detection,&quot; builds on the foundational concepts of neural network architecture and feature enhancement introduced in the parent paper, &quot;Path Aggregation Network for Instance Segmentation.&quot; While the parent paper focuses on improving instance segmentation through path aggregation, the child paper extends this work by incorporating new features and techniques to achieve state-of-the-art results in object detection, demonstrating a progression in the application of advanced neural network strategies.</data>
