      <data key="d4">The child paper builds on the parent paper by proposing an extension to the basic encoder-decoder architecture in neural machine translation, specifically by introducing a mechanism for soft alignment that enhances performance. While the parent paper analyzes the properties of neural machine translation models, the child paper advances this work by addressing limitations and improving the model's effectiveness in translation tasks.</data>
