      <data key="d4">The child paper builds on the parent paper by extending the concepts of training deep networks through a greedy layer-wise approach, which is informed by the optimization challenges discussed in the parent paper regarding training models using contrastive divergence. While the parent paper focuses on the training of products of experts, the child paper empirically explores and enhances the training strategies for deep networks, demonstrating their effectiveness in achieving better optimization and generalization.</data>
