      <data key="d4">The child paper builds on the concepts of deep learning and convolutional networks, which are foundational to the parent paper's discussion of training challenges in neural networks. While the parent paper focuses on recurrent neural networks, the child paper extends the discussion to very deep convolutional networks, applying insights from the parent paper's training strategies to improve image super-resolution performance.</data>
