    <edge source="https://openalex.org/W1485009520" target="https://openalex.org/W1815076433">
      <data key="d3">In 2015, article Convolutional LSTM Network: A Machine Learning Approach for Precipitation Nowcasting was published and referenced article On the difficulty of training Recurrent Neural Networks that was published in 2012</data>
      <data key="d4">The child paper builds on the concepts introduced in the parent paper by utilizing the insights on recurrent neural networks, specifically addressing the challenges of training such networks in the context of precipitation nowcasting through the development of a Convolutional LSTM model. It extends the foundational knowledge of recurrent neural networks to propose a novel approach for improving performance in weather forecasting tasks.</data>
