    <edge source="https://openalex.org/W2019207321" target="https://openalex.org/W2155399784">
      <data key="d3">In 1993, article ANFIS: adaptive-network-based fuzzy inference system was published and referenced article Orthogonal least squares learning algorithm for radial basis function networks that was published in 1991</data>
      <data key="d4">The child paper on ANFIS builds on the concepts introduced in the parent paper regarding neural networks by proposing a hybrid learning procedure that incorporates fuzzy logic and human knowledge, thereby extending the application of adaptive networks in modeling and control systems. Additionally, it compares the performance of ANFIS with traditional artificial neural networks, including those discussed in the parent paper.</data>
