      <data key="d3">In 2000, article Statistical pattern recognition: a review was published and referenced article Neural Networks and the Bias/Variance Dilemma that was published in 1992</data>
      <data key="d4">The child paper builds on the parent paper by reviewing and summarizing key concepts in statistical pattern recognition, including the challenges highlighted in the parent paper regarding neural networks and their limitations in complex pattern recognition tasks. It extends the discussion by incorporating recent developments and applications in the field, while also comparing various methodologies.</data>
